Method
A random sample of 239 pregnant women were interviewed at booking using a detailed sociodemographic history and the Revised Version of the Clinical Interview Schedule (CIS-R). The CIS-R was again administered at 36 weeks and at 8 weeks postpartum to 95.8% of the women.
Results
